                                    <h2>Poems on sustainable AI at my blog "The AI has gone bananas"</h2>
                                </div>


                                <p align=" justify">
                                    I consider myself a statistically rare mix of science and literature constantly
                                    trying to
                                    embrace my
                                    juxtapositions.
                                    Recently this has crystallised in a blog named <a href="https://bananas.ai"><b>The
                                            AI
                                            has
                                            gone
                                            bananas</b></a> where I
                                    write free verse poems (such as <em>"The future of AI is female"</em>) at the
                                    intersection of artificial
                                    intelligence, social issues and environmental sustainability.

